title: Where The Sugar Daddies
itunes:title: Where The Sugar Daddies
description:
Today on the show we opened up the phone lines for our listeners who have 'sugar daddies' and to listen to what their sugar daddies do for them, after Charalamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a woman that couldnt make juror duty because she had to see her sugar daddy.
